--- | ---------------- |\n| &gt; 12.0.0 | 7.4.47 |\n\n## Contributing\n\nSee the [contributing guide](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) to learn how to contribute to the repository and the development workflow.\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}